title: FSX,FSXSE,P3DAerosoft Malpensa LIMC v1.11
description:
I don't know if this will work... the installation file is authentic since I legally bought it. I'm not including my serial and email and such. I've noticed that the one file used for aerosoft seems to work for them all, so I'm including that.


Installation:
Start installation.
When at registration screen press the windows key(flag at bottom)+r
Type in %TEMP%
Sort by date
Go into the most recent one should be a bunch of letters and number.
Go into the folder with a bunch of letters and numbers.
Copy ascrypt_pro.dll there and overwrite.
Go back to installation and click next.
Install as normal.


I believe this is the most recent version. Haven't checked in a while. I got it when it was on sale. Since v1.11 isn't on here I though I'd upload it. Untested. I don't feel like reinstalling since I used my legal stuff. Should work. If not maybe someone can make a crack for it. 

I also have the most recent verson of Cielosim Jacksonville if anyone wants it. It has animated jetways. With default FSX system.

I don't take requests. Feel free to ask one but don't expect me to do it. I search for things when I need them. Should I find something that doesn't exist here I'll upload it.

I don't know if this airport has been updated for P3D v4. This one doesn't support it for sure. I'm not in the mood to check.

If it doesn't work the only two things I can think of is that you didn't install it right or the crack doesn't work for this. It works fine in game. SODE jetways work great. The installation doesn't have that error and subsequent problem that the other version on here has
